thread.title_full: Snapfish.co.uk reviewed by MRS S POLAND

author: MRS S POLAND
title: MRS S POLAND
text: I found the website easy to use, it was easy to upload photies from pc or social media to put into calendar. I liked the idea of changing the dates. I was too late to order at the beginning of January, so I started my calendar from February. Also had a discount code which made my purchase even cheaper!
